              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="question-wrapper">
              <div class="question-content">
                <img src="/img/user.svg" alt="" class="user">
                <div class="question">
                  <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Quam eius dolorum, voluptates illum error voluptatum fugiat praesentium quia facilis aut sint! Mollitia non commodi, dicta laboriosam quam consectetur quasi deserunt?</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="actions">
                <a href="#" class="check" data-id="3">
                  <img src="/img/check.svg" alt="">
